    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/989721468ab8d52868e957fe5a6779b6.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/989721468ab8d52868e957fe5a6779b6.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/989721468ab8d52868e957fe5a6779b6.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>I NEED SPACE</strong></i> is an artfully hand-crafted <i><strong>space adventure</strong></i> game that features a wholesome twist of the <i><strong>sci-fi fantasy</strong></i> genre. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/7b54be093edde5be5e40f1fc1c2d5a3f.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=135 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/c264b9b09ad77b620e31ec1e86f4832f.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/c264b9b09ad77b620e31ec1e86f4832f.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/c264b9b09ad77b620e31ec1e86f4832f.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >with your nebulous companion the <i><strong>Cosmic Cat</strong></i>, and embark on a journey across the sea of stars, to <i><strong>rekindle</strong></i> a dying universe from a mysterious <i><strong>Galactical Pandemic</strong></i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/41128da9a8bab19d99ce6369ecfccde0.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=135 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e0e2f90a505c8cac4b8c163cf5aecb6b.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/ca2f876f0c46a553f46a0579d5615e55.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/02909fcfca8d15b35e4b5e78249d6311.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/02909fcfca8d15b35e4b5e78249d6311.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/02909fcfca8d15b35e4b5e78249d6311.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/97a61823229dfc94d7e7ef8683125fe6.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=167 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/a1d4c9a99ea3cabb0ff23ab043d60657.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/a1d4c9a99ea3cabb0ff23ab043d60657.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/a1d4c9a99ea3cabb0ff23ab043d60657.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/cde0af8be90645fd4bcc4140891b9cfc.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/7f69f4f4eae49bd9f7935a74d4f68e31.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/7f69f4f4eae49bd9f7935a74d4f68e31.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/7f69f4f4eae49bd9f7935a74d4f68e31.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e0e2f90a505c8cac4b8c163cf5aecb6b.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/37de4da8498171f7cb1f77c0104e6cd0.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/d9e91e0515e0df1f4b6cb6ffe5c1cf61.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/2a2b25220954c1292ff4bdb6cbe2eb5a.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/2a2b25220954c1292ff4bdb6cbe2eb5a.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/2a2b25220954c1292ff4bdb6cbe2eb5a.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/bd86e89ed68f46c454bee2284891427e.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e46ef359b15b2342634df2ffc0135d05.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e46ef359b15b2342634df2ffc0135d05.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e46ef359b15b2342634df2ffc0135d05.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/dcfc38e5b9486742e20fee2baf642c2b.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/aad686e6b60ed10b8b5e83a41edaf629.poster.avif?t=1771676545\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/aad686e6b60ed10b8b5e83a41edaf629.webm?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/aad686e6b60ed10b8b5e83a41edaf629.mp4?t=1771676545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e6320f051d348ed016f91b2dcd519c7b.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>I NEED SPACE</strong></i> is a 2D video game artfully designed to be a reflection of <i><strong>critical </strong></i>environmental issues such as; <i><strong>climate change, coastal fracking, deforestation, waste management challenges</strong></i> - all woven into the fabric of a cautionary tale, with the ultimate aspiration of sharing deeper <i><strong>awareness</strong></i> regarding the issues, to encourage players into <i><strong>adopting</strong></i>  eco-friendly lifestyles, and <i><strong>participating</strong></i> in environmental initiatives in real life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is of the utmost importance to note that though the game story is fantastical in nature - our studio ensure credibility and prevent the spread of misleading information by consistently collaborating with local <i><strong>NGOs</strong></i> and subject-matter specialists. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Activation:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10% of launch sales will go towards environmental / animal welfare actions.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% of sales during World Ocean Day month (June) goes towards ocean related collaborations.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% of sales made from Animal/ Cats related events will go towards designated animal shelters.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/2cdfeb00bbf5ab5e1c327697f538e6a1.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=135 /></span>Follow our social media and be the first to know about release dates, sneak peeks, and exclusive offers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also join us on discord and be an Early Explorer to participate in playtests, get exclusive stickers, and get to know the community!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️INSTAGRAM | @i_need_space__game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐️TWITTER | @INeedSpace_game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337180/extras/e6320f051d348ed016f91b2dcd519c7b.avif?t=1771676545\" width=617 height=135 /></span></p>",
